# UITableViewCell.SeparatorStyle.singleLineEtched

**Case**

The separator cell has double lines running across its width, giving it an etched look.

## Declaration

```swift
case singleLineEtched
```

## Discussion

This style is currently only supported for grouped-style table views.

## Constants

- **UITableViewCell.SeparatorStyle.none**: The separator cell has no distinct style.
- **UITableViewCell.SeparatorStyle.singleLine**: The separator cell has a single line running across its width.
